244,249,254,259,294,308,313,318,325,330,335,342,347,359,366,371,376,381,386,393,398,403,410,415,437,442,449,454,461,466,473,478,485,499,504,509,514,521,526,533,538,549,554,561,566,573,580,585,592,597,604,609,616,621,628,633,640,645,652,657,664],{"type":181,"tag":182,"props":183,"children":185},"element","h2",{"id":184},"twitter",[186],{"type":181,"tag":187,"props":188,"children":192},"a",{"href":189,"rel":190},"https://x.com/budibase?utm_campaign=Onboarding&utm_medium=email&_hsenc=p2ANqtz--6Ynd76E4FehE07-MjjIZWwvuH2B-KMkxdBPT1TJ5Eh4ci9Wy0q_RZYTIRBsGXz_09u4n_C8GiUe9f8mFjiC6Dj9B4sw&_hsmi=66516363&utm_content=66516363&utm_source=hs_automation",[191],"nofollow",[193],{"type":194,"value":195},"text","Twitter",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":198,"children":199},"p",{},[200],{"type":194,"value":201},"2020 年那会儿 Budibase 从 SlackHQ 迁移到 Discord，发布了他的第一条推文，尽管点赞数量只有寥寥三个。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":203,"children":204},{},[205],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":207,"children":209},"img",{"alt":175,"src":208},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031913704.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":211,"children":212},{},[213],{"type":194,"value":214},"推崇 Sarah Drasner 的空盒子概念，即“也许我们可以从一个空盒子开始，这个盒子只包含正在解决的问题的核心用例或问题”，而不是看到周围完整的网站或应用而感到自卑。Budibase 认为它是一个空盒子，为用户抽象了构建 Web 应用的复杂性。PRay 也是如此，并且应当在多用户交互上大有改进。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":216,"children":217},{},[218],{"type":194,"value":219},"Joe Johnston（应该是 budibase 成员）在 2020 年发表了 What is custom software development in 2025，讨论了“定制化软件开发”需求的广阔场景。",{"type":181,"tag":221,"props":222,"children":223},"blockquote",{},[224],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":225,"children":226},{},[227],{"type":194,"value":228},"定制软件开发是指为特定问题、用户或人群设计、开发、部署、维护和提供软件支持的过程。理解定制软件开发的关键在于认识到正在开发的解决方案是为单一、特定的目的/问题量身定制的——通常无法通过现有的解决方案来解决。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":230,"children":231},{},[232],{"type":194,"value":233},"SaaS 软件（COTS 商业现货软件）单价比定制低，但远没有定制乃至自建来得灵活。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":235,"children":236},{},[237],{"type":194,"value":238},"“when COTS software did not solve the problem for SMEs, tools like Excel and Access were drafted in and a solution glued together”，Excel 作为从业者的信息交换工具，类似 Python、Lua 在游戏引擎中的胶水作用。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":240,"children":241},{},[242],{"type":194,"value":243},"今天正好是 2025 年 1 月，我认为 budibase 对软件开发的认识很有前瞻性。其观点也符合我的两点认识：第一，软件开发应该面向更广阔的 C 端，在知识爆炸并有势形成超级个体的时代，代码技能（实际上是指通过人机界面制定规则并实现需求）是全民必备的技能；第二，新时代的消费包含了新时代的创造，消费时间不仅仅通过娱乐，也可以包含创造性的方式，如同我的世界、乐高等。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":245,"children":246},{},[247],{"type":194,"value":248},"文章引用了 Percolate、Oribi、Monese 三个工具来说明定制软件如何解决问题，但没用过评价不了。实际上这可能只是为了文章的 SEO。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":250,"children":251},{},[252],{"type":194,"value":253},"2020-10-02 发布了一个暗黑风格的界面，是制作内容的暗黑风格，而不是 budibase 的。其本地的暗黑模式是在 2020-11-06 号发布的（已经过了公测前两周），不过这速度也太快了。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":255,"children":256},{},[257],{"type":194,"value":258},"有人发推推荐了一些产品，包括 budibase，剩下一些可能值得观摩的：",{"type":181,"tag":260,"props":261,"children":262},"ul",{},[263,274,284],{"type":181,"tag":264,"props":265,"children":266},"li",{},[267],{"type":181,"tag":187,"props":268,"children":271},{"href":269,"rel":270},"https://x.com/PoryHQ",[191],[272],{"type":194,"value":273},"PoryHQ",{"type":181,"tag":264,"props":275,"children":276},{},[277],{"type":181,"tag":187,"props":278,"children":281},{"href":279,"rel":280},"https://x.com/bildrHQ",[191],[282],{"type":194,"value":283},"bildrHQ",{"type":181,"tag":264,"props":285,"children":286},{},[287],{"type":181,"tag":187,"props":288,"children":291},{"href":289,"rel":290},"https://x.com/draftbit",[191],[292],{"type":194,"value":293},"draftbit",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":295,"children":296},{},[297,299,306],{"type":194,"value":298},"有个 Tag 叫做 ",{"type":181,"tag":300,"props":301,"children":303},"code",{"className":302},[],[304],{"type":194,"value":305},"#100DaysOfNoCode",{"type":194,"value":307},"，看着不错。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":309,"children":310},{},[311],{"type":194,"value":312},"Bubibase 推荐了 Martin McKeveney 的 NoSQL 和 DynamoDB 的演讲。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":314,"children":315},{},[316],{"type":194,"value":317},"展示了一些预制的渐变色（UI 还可以优化）：",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":319,"children":320},{},[321],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":322,"children":324},{"alt":175,"src":323},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031950748.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":326,"children":327},{},[328],{"type":194,"value":329},"2020-10-22 发布了不推荐生产环境使用的公共测试版本。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":331,"children":332},{},[333],{"type":194,"value":334},"在什么是你建 Web App 时最喜欢的工作内容时，没有人投票给“测试”。不过，反向思考，能辅助用户做测试的工具可能也是很有市场的。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":336,"children":337},{},[338],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":339,"children":341},{"alt":175,"src":340},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031954506.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":343,"children":344},{},[345],{"type":194,"value":346},"TechCrunch 的一篇 The No-Code Generation is arriving 文章中，根据“In the distant past, there was a proverbial “digital divide” that bifurcated workers into those who knew how to use computers and those who didn’t.”推演了今后数据分析工程在今后可能作为新的“数字鸿沟”出现以及带来的影响。而这正是过去几年（2017~2020）低代码发力的方向，AirTable 和 Retool 这种年轻的公司分别以 26 亿以及 10 亿美元的估值崛起。文章还提到了“而像 Bildr、Shogun、Bubble、Stacker”等公司，但是我没有用过。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":348,"children":349},{},[350,357],{"type":181,"tag":187,"props":351,"children":354},{"href":352,"rel":353},"https://nocodelist.co/",[191],[355],{"type":194,"value":356},"NocodeList",{"type":194,"value":358},"，收集了 300+ 无代码工具，而他本身就是一个很适合无代码建设的网站。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":360,"children":361},{},[362],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":363,"children":365},{"alt":175,"src":364},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032006061.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":367,"children":368},{},[369],{"type":194,"value":370},"数据看起来还不错，两周的公测信息。公测后两周的数据没有前两周好看。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":372,"children":373},{},[374],{"type":194,"value":375},"🔻 606 downloads\n🤖 619 apps created\n🚀 246 apps deployed",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":377,"children":378},{},[379],{"type":194,"value":380},"在公测第三个月时，bb 积累了 3200+ 用户、2400+ 应用，以及 554 个部署的应用。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":382,"children":383},{},[384],{"type":194,"value":385},"2020-11-09 发布的图表功能，第一版的功能比较简单，但是很有视觉风格：",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":387,"children":388},{},[389],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":390,"children":392},{"alt":175,"src":391},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032011651.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":394,"children":395},{},[396],{"type":194,"value":397},"2020-12-20 称自己是“open organization”，可以在 Github 上看到他们的项目路线图，甚至是参与讨论。这种事情（类似完成度的产品）在国内就算放到 2025 年也很难想象。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":399,"children":400},{},[401],{"type":194,"value":402},"2020-12-09 在 budibase，15 分钟就能创造一个 Winamp 风格的界面。也许包括功能？链接打不开了，无法验证。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":404,"children":405},{},[406],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":407,"children":409},{"alt":175,"src":408},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032144479.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":411,"children":412},{},[413],{"type":194,"value":414},"“将 Star 数量视为开源社区的货币”这一信念让 Joe Johnston 开始 budibase 的 Github 星星之旅。在 11~12 月间，其数量从 83 个增长到了接近 500，在图上来看这就是指数级别的增长！在博客中分享了其做法。时间来到次年 2 月，Star 数量超过 2000，两倍超越了他们的去年的既定目标。",{"type":181,"tag":260,"props":416,"children":417},{},[418,422,427,432],{"type":181,"tag":264,"props":419,"children":420},{},[421],{"type":194,"value":195},{"type":181,"tag":264,"props":423,"children":424},{},[425],{"type":194,"value":426},"邮件引导指向 Github 并告知路线图、代码都在 Github",{"type":181,"tag":264,"props":428,"children":429},{},[430],{"type":194,"value":431},"budibase 制作的项目支持 Github 调用",{"type":181,"tag":264,"props":433,"children":434},{},[435],{"type":194,"value":436},"更新 Readme",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":438,"children":439},{},[440],{"type":194,"value":441},"而他们新的 Readme 也确实很有吸引力（“Build business apps 50x faster”）：",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":443,"children":444},{},[445],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":446,"children":448},{"alt":175,"src":447},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032149799.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":450,"children":451},{},[452],{"type":194,"value":453},"“As companies, we often look outwards for growth, but looking inwards can provide opportunities. Optimizing processes, analyzing data, & equipping staff with the right tools is often an easier win for many companies; this is where low-code platforms will continue to succeed.”，最有意思的配图。包括上文提到的 2025 软件定制需求前瞻一文中的配图，都是相同类型的矢量图，很有意思。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":455,"children":456},{},[457],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":458,"children":460},{"alt":175,"src":459},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032152157.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":462,"children":463},{},[464],{"type":194,"value":465},"2021 年初，关于希望使用哪个平台托管 bb，居然没有 AWS。前两名 Heroku 和 DigitalOcean 几乎占据了 100% 的投票。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":467,"children":468},{},[469],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":470,"children":472},{"alt":175,"src":471},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032154794.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":474,"children":475},{},[476],{"type":194,"value":477},"还有另一个投票也显示了 Twitter 上用户的数据库偏好，第一名居然是 Google Sheets。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":479,"children":480},{},[481],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":482,"children":484},{"alt":175,"src":483},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032156394.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":486,"children":487},{},[488,490,497],{"type":194,"value":489},"推荐了一个如何启动开源项目并扩大其影响力的网站，里面有一系列文章：",{"type":181,"tag":187,"props":491,"children":494},{"href":492,"rel":493},"https://opensource.guide/",[191],[495],{"type":194,"value":496},"Open Source Guides",{"type":194,"value":498},"。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":500,"children":501},{},[502],{"type":194,"value":503},"Tech Nation 的 Rising Stars 3 奖项包含了 bb。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":505,"children":506},{},[507],{"type":194,"value":508},"2021-04-13 招聘 3 名 JavaScript 工程师。基于之前他发过关于 Svelte 的迷因，我猜创始人对 Svelte 依旧比较感兴趣。同月 25 号，bb 赞助了 Svelte Summit。直到次年 1 月，他们才开始招聘产品负责人、JS 工程师、产品教育经历、产品设计和客户成功经理，可见扩张得比较节制。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":510,"children":511},{},[512],{"type":194,"value":513},"那么，下一步是什么？我也想问。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":515,"children":516},{},[517],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":518,"children":520},{"alt":175,"src":519},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032244873.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":522,"children":523},{},[524],{"type":194,"value":525},"百姓网的知识库里面也有很多内部应用，但是年久失修。我管他们叫幽灵应用。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":527,"children":528},{},[529],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":530,"children":532},{"alt":175,"src":531},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032251644.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":534,"children":535},{},[536],{"type":194,"value":537},"2021-10-22 发布了新的响应式拖拽，看起来用户体验很好。PRay 马上跟进。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":539,"children":540},{},[541],{"type":181,"tag":542,"props":543,"children":546},"video",{"src":544,"controls":174,"width":545},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032256999.mp4","100%",[547],{"type":194,"value":548},"Your browser does not support the video tag.",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":550,"children":551},{},[552],{"type":194,"value":553},"不过 bb 的界面很总是看起来很“Notion”。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":555,"children":556},{},[557],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":558,"children":560},{"alt":175,"src":559},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032308303.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":562,"children":563},{},[564],{"type":194,"value":565},"2021-11-16 日，“经过两年的开发，我们激动的宣布正式在 product hunt 上进行官方宣传”。而他们的商业化也确实非常成功。2022-10-03 甚至创办了 5000 刀的低代码马拉松。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":567,"children":568},{},[569],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":570,"children":572},{"alt":175,"src":571},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032310378.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":574,"children":575},{},[576],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":577,"children":579},{"alt":175,"src":578},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032318431.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":581,"children":582},{},[583],{"type":194,"value":584},"这一切可能都归功于低代码的魔法。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":586,"children":587},{},[588],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":589,"children":591},{"alt":175,"src":590},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032320756.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":593,"children":594},{},[595],{"type":194,"value":596},"其中有非常长的一段时间，他们的 Twitter 都是围绕推广和新闻展开，没有其他内容的讨论。直到 2022-11 左右。此时，他们拿到了 @SignalFire 领投的 700 万美元融资。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":598,"children":599},{},[600],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":601,"children":603},{"alt":175,"src":602},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032316070.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":605,"children":606},{},[607],{"type":194,"value":608},"拿到融资后，Belfast 决定扩大团队规模。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":610,"children":611},{},[612],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":613,"children":615},{"alt":175,"src":614},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032326207.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":617,"children":618},{},[619],{"type":194,"value":620},"Joe Johnston 解释了为何要从 nocode 转型 lowcode。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":622,"children":623},{},[624],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":625,"children":627},{"alt":175,"src":626},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032329318.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":629,"children":630},{},[631],{"type":194,"value":632},"2023 年有许多更新，比如键盘操作，ISO 27001 认证等。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":634,"children":635},{},[636],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":637,"children":639},{"alt":175,"src":638},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032336236.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":641,"children":642},{},[643],{"type":194,"value":644},"最近一年更新了许多教程，这段时间他们对外宣称自己是“表单创建工具”，并且在博客上也两次拿其他表单创建工具做对比。期间放出不少有意思的应用展示，比如 GPT 克隆（2024-03-11）：",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":646,"children":647},{},[648],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":649,"children":651},{"alt":175,"src":650},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032340672.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":653,"children":654},{},[655],{"type":194,"value":656},"在商业化上变得更加大胆，比如推出 Paid Only 功能。",{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":658,"children":659},{},[660],{"type":181,"tag":206,"props":661,"children":663},{"alt":175,"src":662},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032343927.png",[],{"type":181,"tag":197,"props":665,"children":666},{},[667],{"type":194,"value":668},"在最近（2024-11）的 3.0 更新中，他们解释了之后的路线，主要会包含 AI 相关功能的改进。",{"title":175,"searchDepth":670,"depth":670,"links":671},2,[672],{"id":184,"depth":670,"text":195},"markdown","content:6.maps:_products:budibase.md","content","6.maps/_products/budibase.md","6.maps/_products/budibase","md",[680,684],{"_path":681,"title":682,"description":683},"/maps/_products/bit","Bit","Bit 是一个组件驱动的开发工具，它可以帮助我们更好地管理组件。",{"_path":685,"title":686,"description":687},"/maps/_products/dynamo","Dynamo","Dynamo 原本是 Revit 中建筑信息模型 (BIM) 的附加模块，后来发展成熟，成为一个给设计师探索可视化编程、解决问题并自行制作工具的平台。",1771214213892]